{
  "stem": "20711.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because we happened to be under German influence, anybody who was running away from the German side of Poland, they escaped to the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But anybody who was supposedly occupied by the Russians and was anti-communist, they had to go to the western side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And Hungary considered to be one of those.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And trainload of refugees was coming in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when my mom the first time heard it on the radio there is a train passing by in our closest railroad station, which was Mezokeresztes, he convinced my-- or she convinced my father to buy a lot of cigarettes and chocolates, basket full of it.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And she went to the railroad station and waited for the train to come in and give it out to people as presents.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And she spotted a very nice young boy who was two year older than my brother, a nice blond, blue-eyed kids, and she felt very sorry for him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she contacted the Red Cross if we can take him and perhaps his whole family into our custody so they wouldn't have to go into refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they told us it would be very difficult.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But they told us also they going to station them next to our town in an other small little village which had like a Boy Scout camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they turned that camp into a refugee camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So this whole trainload of people eventually wind up next door to us, and we were able to visit them daily.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went with my parents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually my mother was able to receive permission to take this young man, who was, as I said, about 12 at the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Jan Podehovich.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, don't bother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- but we named him [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
